        dc:description           "FIG. 1. — Distribution map of the Niphargus species.Localities are labelled as:1, N. persicus Esmaeili-Rineh,Sari,Fišer & Bargrizaneh,2017 (Mansurkhani Spring); 2, N. yasujensis n. sp. (Chonarestan Spring); 3, N. yasujensis n. sp. (Khong Spring); 4, N. yasujensis n. sp. (Biareh Spring); 5, N. nasrullahi n. sp. (Nahr Spring); 6, N. sharifii Esmaeili-Rineh, Sari & Fišer 2015; 7, N. darvishi Esmaeili-Rineh,Sari & Fišer 2015; 8, N. borisi Esmaeili-Rineh, Sari & Fišer 2015 (Belqais population); 9, N. borisi (Siah population); 10, N. persicus." ;
